<%# Hides the post-command dots for synchronous fast-paths that open a sidebar
    and run no async job (themes/resume/games-import/game-picker). The dots
    appear on `pito:submitted`; without an async ChatDispatchJob nothing
    broadcasts `pito:done`, so we emit it here. The pito--done-dispatch
    controller fires the event on connect; the element is ephemeral (cleared
    the next time #pito-sidebar is updated). %>
<%= turbo_stream.append "pito-sidebar" do %>
  <div data-controller="pito--done-dispatch"
       data-pito--done-dispatch-event-name-value="pito:done"></div>
<% end %>
